[[ja:エロマンガ先生]]
[[zh:埃罗芒阿老师]]

'''''Eromanga Sensei''''' (Japanese:'''{{lj|エロマンガ{{Ruby|先生|せんせい}}}}''') is a [[light novel]] written by [[Tsukasa Fushimi]], and has derivative works.
==Original Work Info==
The light novel is written by Tsukasa Fushimi and illustrated by Hiro Kanzaki. 
===Plot===
Masamune Izumi is a light novel author in high school. His artist, known only as "Eromanga Sensei" is reliable but Masamune has never met him and assumes he's just a perverted otaku. Masamune's little sister is Sagiri, a shut-in girl who hasn't left her room for an entire year. She even forces her brother to make and bring her meals when she stomps the floor. Masamune wants his sister to leave her room, because the two of them are each other's only family.

One day Masamune discovers that Eromanga Sensei and Sagiri are one in the same. Further chaos erupts between the siblings when a beautiful, female, best-selling shōjo manga creator becomes their rival. <ref>https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=18142</ref>

